---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="South Portland Dispensary Guide | Maine Dispensary Guide" description="Complete guide to opening a cannabis dispensary in South Portland, Maine. Portland metro market with lower costs.">
  <article>
    <header>
      <h1>South Portland Dispensary Guide</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">How to open a cannabis dispensary in South Portland, Maine</p>
    </header>

    <section>
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>South Portland, part of the Portland metro area with 25,000+ residents, offers access to the larger Portland market with more affordable real estate costs. Located just across the Casco Bay Bridge, it provides excellent accessibility while avoiding some of Portland's premium costs.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>South Portland Market</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Factor</th><th>Assessment</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Population</td><td>25,000+ (130k+ metro)</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Advantage</td><td>Portland metro access</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Competition</td><td>Moderate</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Real Estate</td><td>Moderate ($15-25/sq ft)</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Regulations</td><td>South Portland has local rules</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Why South Portland?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Portland Metro</strong> - Access to larger market</li>
        <li><strong>Lower Costs</strong> - More affordable than Portland proper</li>
        <li><strong>Good Traffic</strong> - Major arterials through city</li>
        <li><strong>Growing Area</strong> - New development</li>
        <li><strong>Tourist Adjacent</strong> - Near beaches and attractions</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Best Locations in South Portland</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Main Street</strong> - Commercial core</li>
        <li><strong>Broadway</strong> - High traffic corridor</li>
        <li><strong>Payless Plaza area</strong> - Shopping district</li>
        <li><strong>Jetport area</strong> - Near airport, high visibility</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Investment Requirements</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Category</th><th>Estimated Cost</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Real Estate (lease)</td><td>$3,000-5,000/mo</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Build-out</td><td>$100,000-200,000</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Total Investment</td><td>$400,000-800,000</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Local Regulations</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Check South Portland zoning requirements</li>
        <li>Local license may be required</li>
        <li>Distance requirements from schools</li>
        <li>Signage restrictions apply</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="disclaimer">
      <p><em>This is for informational purposes only.</em></p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  article { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
  header { margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .subtitle { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-text-light); }
  section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section h2 { margin-top: 0; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1rem 0; }
  th, td { padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  th { background: var(--color-background); }
  ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .disclaimer { background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffc107; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; }
</style>
